messages.content: What is the purpose of the ComfyUI_FastVAEDecorder_SDXL node?
The ComfyUI_FastVAEDecorder_SDXL node allows users to quickly preview SDXL 1.0 latents in ComfyUI.
What is the ComfyUI_FastVAEDecorder_SDXL node based on?
The ComfyUI_FastVAEDecorder_SDXL node is based on the code from the GitHub repository https://github.com/Birch-san/diffusers-play/tree/main/approx_vae.
